data.description: Welcome Home! Here is your chance to own a home that is the perfect location to all that Jacksonville has to offer. This home features privacy, natural light, an additional garage for extra storage, 4 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms. The kitchen has been recently updated with granite countertops and plenty of cabinet space.  Downstairs also has an extra living room/office for extra space for entertaining. Enjoy lounging in the family room with the electric fireplace or sitting on your screened porch within the privacy of your fully fenced backyard. The upstairs features 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Bring your toys as there are no HOA or CDD fees! Schedule your showing today as this one won't last long.
